{"tid":658324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔鬼身材 龍心面孔]側奶妹PO正面照反擊網友 : 看看自己長什麼雞巴樣","createTime":"2018-05-09T01:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T02:46:41.000Z","uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d20506caf0bdc6013acbdff7f343781c2330f83","tid":658324,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_687bd4adfd5dcba499dc1d7a1d423d77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_687bd4adfd5dcba499dc1d7a1d423d77.jpg&h=01a538f5&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n昨日「側奶妹」接受《蘋果》專訪時，<span style=\"color: red;\">就霸氣比出中指，回敬酸民。</span>而她在臉書上也貼文寫道：「<span style=\"color: red;\">他媽我到底得罪誰了，出門看個房子、買個飲料而已難道還要濃妝豔抹畫的跟蕭機掰一樣才能穿這樣出門嗎？</span>」<br />\n<br />\n她也反擊女房仲和酸民：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我根本不care是哪個Bitch在我講話時這麼近的把我拍的醜的那麼極致，只是鄉民再不看自己長什麼雞巴樣就來批評人會下地獄的噢！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_174f8a8e2248aab0f7412a90bf34c9d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_174f8a8e2248aab0f7412a90bf34c9d4.jpg&h=8d189b04&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_88b714c6f73818f74bf785b12e38ad3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_88b714c6f73818f74bf785b12e38ad3f.jpg&h=675d4721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_be59d3c1b8e1acd99d98b1ee58f68284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_be59d3c1b8e1acd99d98b1ee58f68284.jpg&h=dc493481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_b5f9f3